# hledger-add.meta
# Fires hledger add interactively on completion of +txn/+acct tasks or tasks starting with a trigger verb (pay, buy). Pre-fills date and payee from task description; maps TW project/priority/tags to hledger inline tags. Annotates task with ledger reference on success.

